<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN245-intro">tiṇai, pāṭāṇṭiṇai; tuṟai, kaiyaṟunilai. cēramāṉ kōṭṭampalattut tuñciya mākkōtai taṉ peruṅkōppeṇṭu tuñciya kālaic colliya pāṭṭu.
    <app>
    <lem wit="#C3 #C8">cēramāṉ</lem>
    <rdg wit="#C2">ituvumatu - cēramāṉ</rdg>
    </app> kōṭṭampalattut tuñciya mākkōtai taṉ peruṅkōppeṇṭu tuñciya kālaic colliya pāṭṭu. 
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN245">
<l>yāṅkupperi tāyiṉu nōyaḷa veṉaittē</l>
<l>yuyircekuk kallā matukait taṉmaiyiṟ</l>
<l>kaḷḷi pōkiya kaḷariyam paṟantalai</l>
<l>veḷḷiṭaip pottiya viḷaiviṟa kīmat</l>
<l>toḷḷaḻaṟ paḷḷip pāyal cērtti</l>
<l>ñāṅkar māyntaṉaḷ maṭantai</l>
<l>yiṉṉum vāḻva leṉṉitaṉ paṇpē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>However big it may be, what is the measure of [my] pain,</l>
<l>because of the nature of [my] strength, not [enough] to destroy [my] life?</l>
<l>On the burning ground, saline, overgrown with spurge,</l>
<l>in the open space, on the funeral pyre with mature firewood to cover [it],</l>
<l>being put to sleep on a bed of bright fire,</l>
<l>[my] girl hereafter is gone.</l>
<l>Even now I live. What is the point of this?  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
